OL,3,CMan sets up fundraiser for 'gentle
OL,4,Cgiant' doorman left severely disabled
OL,6,FA man from Plymouth is fundraising for
OL,7,Fa former doorman described as a
OL,8,F"gentle giant" who was left severely
OL,9,Fdisabled after suffering a stroke.
OL,11,FMichael Whitlock set up a GoFundMe
OL,12,Fpage for Adrian Jarvis, from Elburton,
OL,13,Fwho is being cared for by his family
OL,14,Fafter having a stroke several years
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FThe fundraiser has been set up with
OL,18,Fthe goal of raising #2,000 to offer
OL,19,Ffinancial support to Adrian's family.
