OL,3,CMan sets up fundraiser for 'gentle
OL,4,Cgiant' doorman left severely disabled
OL,6,F"This is the second fundraiser I have
OL,7,Fset up in recent years, the first one
OL,8,Fwas to build a conservatory to give
OL,9,FAdrian a bit of space and outside
OL,10,Fliving.
OL,12,F"This is our way of appreciating the
OL,13,Ftimes we shared with the big man and
OL,14,Fsomehow showing some respect as a
OL,15,Ffinal farewell!
OL,17,F"Please if it's only a few pounds give
OL,18,Fto this man's cause and help relieve
OL,19,Fsome of the stress for the family at
OL,20,Fthis sad and heartbreaking event."
